ium wp-image-1196597 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.34-609x580.png" alt="" width="609" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.34-609x580.png 609w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.34-768x731.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.34.png 836w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 609px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1196598 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.41-612x580.png" alt="" width="612" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.41-612x580.png 612w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.41-768x727.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.41.png 868w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 612px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1196605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.57-694x406.png" alt="" width="694" height="406" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.57-694x406.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.57-1280x749.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.57-768x449.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.57-1536x898.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-29-11.08.57.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />（图片来源：<a href="https://www.vmall.com/product/10086302291465.html?cid=228609">华为商城</a>）</p><p>截至截稿时间，在华为商城已有约 185 万人预购了华为 Mate60 RS 非凡大师。此外，该商品也在其他电商平台开始预购。</p><p>据了解，华为 Mate60 RS 非凡大师是 ULTIMATE DESIGN 推出的首款手机产品，采用陶瓷和金属作为后盖材质，而红色陶瓷版本手机的陶瓷是稀有陶瓷，更加入了二氧化铈稀土元素，经过 50 余道制作工序才制成。此外，该产品还采用了四曲荧幕技术、玄武钢化昆仑玻璃等。</p><p>日前，华为在深圳召开秋季全场景新品发表会，华为 MatePad Pro、超高阶品牌「非凡大师」、黄金智慧腕表等新品集体亮相。著名艺人刘德华也出席了华为发布会，并担任华为 Mate 60 RS 非凡大师品牌大使。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.163.com/dy/article/IFKTOQGN0512B07B.html">163</a>、<a href="https://kan.china.com/article/2891005.html">kan.china</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
