            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1195615</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Elon Musk 今日于 X（前称 Twitter）表示将会于香港时间今日下午 2 点测试 X 的直播功能。身为 X 老板兼电玩爱好者的 Elon Musk 称由于太多人要求直播电玩，所以他将会他将会 Speedrun Diablo 4 的等级 99 恶梦地城。</p><p>Elon Musk 表示会于香港时间今日下午 2 点测试 X 的直播功能 ，更会额外增加游戏难度，称在挑战 Speedrun 时不会配戴 Malignant Hearts。</p><p>Malignant Hearts 是 Diablo 4 Season 1 推出的新道具，总共有 32 种，其获得方式为击杀怪物获得。Maligant Hearts 性质类似 Diablo 3 的传奇宝石，可在饰品槽装配，且会为玩家带来极强的加成。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/333-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/333-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/333.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：abmedia</p><p>虽然 Elon Musk 称会 Speedrun，但他亦「戴定头盔」，表示其 Speedrun 仅是以业余玩家的标准计算，呼吁观众不要有太高期望。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Will test X livestream scaling tonight at ~11pm CT with some silly stuff.</p><p>People have asked me to stream myself playing video games, so I will try to speedrun a Tier 99 Nightmare dungeon on Diablo (with no malignant hearts).</p><p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1707191641914671117?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 28, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>直播连结：<a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk">https://twitter.com/elonmusk</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.sportskeeda.com/esports/news-elon-musk-slated-speedrun-diablo-4-nightmare-dungeons-x-test-new-live-streaming-feature">Sportskeeda</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1707191641914671117">X</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
